  • Classes in org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph used by org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph 
    Class and Description
    AbstractSparseGraphBuilder
    An abstract GraphBuilder implementation to build graphs that extend from SparseGraph.
    Edge
    Basic representation of an undirected and unweighted edge.
    EdgeDecorator
    Decorator class for any type of Edge.
    Graph
    Basic representation of a mathematical graph.
    GraphBuilder
    A GraphBuilder allows to create and modify graphs.
    GraphFactory
    A graph factory is responsible for instantiating new graphs, vertices and edges.
    GraphProjection
    This class allows to extract subgraphs from existing graphs by projecting specific vertices and edges onto a new graph.
    GraphProjectionBuilder
    An GraphBuilder implementation to build graph projections.
    GraphProjectionFactory
    A graph projection factory is responsible for instantiating new graph projections, vertex decorators and edge decorators.
    SparseEdge
    Representation of an undirected and unweighted edge.
    SparseGraph
    Representation of an undirected and unweighted mathematical sparse graph.
    SparseVertex
    Representation of a vertex without any further attributes.
    Vertex
    Basic representation of a vertex.
    VertexDecorator
    Decorator class for any type of Vertex.
